                <b>Enterprise NAID AAA Compliance Management:</b><br/>
                ‚Ä¢ üéñÔ∏è Complete NAID AAA/AA/A certification tracking<br/>
                ‚Ä¢ üîç Automated audit scheduling and management<br/>
                ‚Ä¢ üìú Digital certificate generation and tracking<br/>
                ‚Ä¢ üõ°Ô∏è Comprehensive security standards compliance<br/>
                ‚Ä¢ üë• Multi-level personnel security verification<br/>
                ‚Ä¢ üìä Real-time performance metrics and analytics<br/>
                ‚Ä¢ üîî Proactive expiry and renewal notifications<br/>
                ‚Ä¢ üìã Detailed compliance checklists and workflows<br/>
                ‚Ä¢ üîó Integration with destruction and shredding services
            </p>
        </field>
    </record>
</data>
</odoo>
